STATE
v.
WORLEY 2018-0757 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 27, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellant's motion for extension of time to transmit record. Motion granted. The record shall be filed no later than February 11, 2019. No additional motions for extension of time to transmit the record shall be filed.
